metadata.name: Interlude
metadata.description:
'Astronimals Series' where gilded objects such as fish heads, animal bones and wood were used as matter, reimagined as extraterrestrial lifeforms and space vessels. All captured in-camera with no digital manipulation.

The series was created in 2011 and won a Honorable Mention in the International Photography Awards in the Fine Art / Still Life category in 2013.

All the works in the series comes verified by Verisart and includes an individual Certificates of Authenticity on the blockchain which will be transferred to the collector.   

The total number of works in this series is 20.
